# ðŸ§¾ django-finacc

**Plug-and-Play Financial Accounting for Django** â€” a reusable **double-entry bookkeeping** engine with REST APIs, period locking, GST/VAT support, and chart of accounts templates.

> Works with Django 5.x and Python 3.11+.  
> Built for modular integration into ERP, CRM, or eCommerce projects.

---

## ðŸš€ Features

- ðŸ§® **True Double-Entry Accounting** â€” balanced journal entries enforced at DB level  
- ðŸ§‘â€ðŸ’¼ **Multi-Company** & **Multi-Currency** (with FX rate tables)  
- ðŸ§¾ **Chart of Accounts (CoA)** templates (India GST ready)  
- ðŸ§· **Period Locking & Year Close** helpers  
- ðŸ’° **GST/VAT Tax Models** â€” inclusive/exclusive with CGST/SGST/IGST splits  
- âš™ï¸ **DRF APIViews** â€” clean JSON endpoints for accounting automation  
- ðŸ“Š **Trial Balance / Ledger Helpers**  
- ðŸ” **Immutable Entries** (reversal-only edits, planned)  
- ðŸ§± **Plug-and-Play** â€” drop into any Django project as an app  

